Class Ticket

java.lang.Object
main.java.UEFS.system.model.Ticket
public class Ticket extends Object
Represents a ticket for an event in the system. Each ticket is associated with an event, has a unique identifier, a status, price, and code.

      public Ticket(Event event, Double price, String code)

      Parameters:
      event - the event associated with the ticket
      price - the price of the ticket
      code - the unique code of the ticket

    • Ticket

      public Ticket(Event event, String code)
      Constructs a new Ticket with the specified event and code. The ticket price is set to 0.0 and the status is set to active by default.
      Parameters:
      event - the event associated with the ticket
      code - the unique code of the ticket
